{"entity": "Union Data Protection Law", "type": "concept", "description": "The legal framework of the European Union governing the processing of personal data.<SEP>The overarching legal framework of the European Union governing the protection of personal data and the rights of data subjects.<SEP>Union data protection law governs the sharing and processing of personal data, including within the AI regulatory sandbox."}
